{"word":"G1736 - ἐνδημέω - endēméō - en-day-meh'-o - Be at home","slug":"G1736","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνδημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>endēméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>en-day-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be at home"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03B4;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - ende&#x0304;meo&#x0304;</b> - <i>en-day-meh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G1218\">G1218</a>; to <i>be in</i> one&rsquo;s own <i>country</i>, that is, <i>home</i> (figuratively): - be at home (present)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1218\">G1218</a>, <a href=\"#/G1553\">G1553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3927\">G3927</a>"}]}